{
  "stem": "2723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My sister wasn't against it, but I think it was definitely me taking charge.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In her last letter to me, my mother puts me in charge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I have that letter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I explained to Gustav why I wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't think he minded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I think he was hugely relieved, and I'm not blaming him for it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we arranged an evening when this man-- the second one-- would pick us up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Under cover of darkness, we went just as we were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We had nothing, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We had no more clothes left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I-- I remember we wore coats already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And it was a long walk, and what I do clearly remember was that the streets were extremely busy with uniforms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It just seemed very obvious that it wasn't an ordinary night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "There were far more arm-banded Slavic Hlinka guards, which was the people that we feared so much, in the streets.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "A lot of German soldiers in the streets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the man just urged us to walk as fast as we could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Naturally, we wore no stars, you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we walked for at least 3/4 of an hour 'til we reached this club, which was in a-- AN outer part of Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Pretty, and we were absolutely enchanted when we reached the club itself, which was an isolated situation at one corner of a large block of land.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And inside, really, it was paradise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I mean, we couldn't turn the light on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We had to be very careful not to flush toilets during the day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We couldn't run water during the day, but it had, really, a very lush-- compared to where we had been-- luxurious feel to it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "A proper bed for each of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
